evaluation_data.role_requirements:
For the role of a Senior Machine Learning Engineer, here are the relevant technical skills, programming languages, frameworks, and tools:

LANGUAGES: 
- Python
- R
- SQL
- Java/Scala (for big data processing)

FRAMEWORKS: 
- TensorFlow
- PyTorch
- scikit-learn
- Keras
- XGBoost
- LightGBM
- Apache Spark (for distributed data processing)

TOOLS: 
- Jupyter Notebook
- MLflow (for model tracking and management)
- Docker (for containerization)
- Kubernetes (for orchestration)
- Git (for version control)
- Apache Airflow (for workflow management)
- TensorBoard (for visualization)
- Pandas (for data manipulation)
- NumPy (for numerical computations)

KEYWORDS: 
- Machine Learning
- Deep Learning
- Natural Language Processing (NLP)
- Computer Vision
- Reinforcement Learning
- Feature Engineering
- Model Deployment
- Hyperparameter Tuning
- Data Preprocessing
- A/B Testing
- Big Data
- Cloud ML Services (AWS SageMaker, Google AI Platform, Azure ML)
